          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-1722596594736-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>to the pan<strong> </strong>with 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for 10-12 min further or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-copy-1722596608787-x200.jpg",
