            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>creamy walnut chicken satsivi </strong>next to the <strong>cooked rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining ground smoked paprika</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>quick-pickled shallot salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
